Description:

Developed an advanced GPS Tracking System within the SMART ERP platform using ASP.NET MVC 5, C#, SQL Server, 
jQuery, and Google Maps integration. Implemented real-time employee live location tracking, field visit monitoring, 
and route history management with browser/mobile geolocation support. Designed modules for Field Visit GPS logging, 
Live Employee Tracking, GPS History, and admin monitoring dashboards with role-based access control. Integrated latitude,
longitude, accuracy, visit purpose, client details, and timestamp-based tracking to support operational monitoring, 
employee movement analysis, and field activity management.Ensured secure, scalable, and responsive implementation compatible 
with both desktop and mobile environments.
